<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Duel of Muskets 4 - 2 Player FPS</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { 
            overflow: hidden; 
            background: #000; 
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
        #gameContainer {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
        }
        #instructions {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
            border: 2px solid #8B4513;
            padding: 30px;
            color: #D2B48C;
            text-align: center;
            z-index: 1000;
            max-width: 800px;
        }
        #instructions h1 {
            color: #FFD700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
        }
        .controls-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 30px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .player-controls {
            background: rgba(139, 69, 19, 0.3);
            padding: 15px;
            border: 1px solid #8B4513;
        }
        .player-controls h3 {
            color: #FFD700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .key {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #333;
            border: 1px solid #666;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            margin: 2px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        #startBtn {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #8B4513 0%, #654321 100%);
            border: 2px solid #FFD700;
            color: #FFD700;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            font-size: 20px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        #startBtn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #A0522D 0%, #8B4513 100%);
        }
        #hud1, #hud2 {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 50%;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        #hud1 { top: 0; }
        #hud2 { bottom: 0; }
        .hud-content {
            position: absolute;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #FFD700;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
        }
        #hud1 .hud-content { top: 10px; left: 10px; }
        #hud2 .hud-content { bottom: 10px; left: 10px; }
        .health-bar {
            width: 200px;
            height: 20px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
            border: 2px solid #8B4513;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .health-fill {
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #8B0000 0%, #FF0000 100%);
            transition: width 0.3s;
        }
        .reload-indicator {
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .state-display {
            color: #87CEEB;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .crosshair {
            position: absolute;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255,215,0,0.8);
            border-radius: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .crosshair::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 4px;
            height: 4px;
            background: #FFD700;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        }
        #winner {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.95);
            border: 3px solid #FFD700;
            padding: 50px;
            color: #FFD700;
            text-align: center;
            z-index: 2000;
            display: none;
        }
        #winner h2 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        #restartBtn {
            background: #8B4513;
            border: 2px solid #FFD700;
            color: #FFD700;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="gameContainer"></div>
    
    <div id="instructions">
        <h1>⚔️ DUEL OF MUSKETS 4 ⚔️</h1>
        <p>Face your opponent in a deadly duel. Load your musket, aim true, and fire!</p>
        
        <div class="controls-grid">
            <div class="player-controls">
                <h3>🔵 PLAYER 1 (Top Screen)</h3>
                <p><span class="key">W</span><span class="key">A</span><span class="key">S</span><span class="key">D</span> - Move</p>
                <p><span class="key">Q</span><span class="key">E</span> - Rotate Musket</p>
                <p><span class="key">X</span> - Hold to Aim Iron Sights</p>
                <p><span class="key">F</span> - Fire (when ready)</p>
                <p><span class="key">R</span> - Reload / Next Step</p>
            </div>
            <div class="player-controls">
                <h3>🔴 PLAYER 2 (Bottom Screen)</h3>
                <p><span class="key">I</span><span class="key">J</span><span class="key">K</span><span class="key">L</span> - Move</p>
                <p><span class="key">U</span><span class="key">O</span> - Rotate Musket</p>
                <p><span class="key">M</span> - Hold to Aim Iron Sights</p>
                <p><span class="key">N</span> - Fire (when ready)</p>
                <p><span class="key">H</span> - Reload / Next Step</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #999;">
            Reloading Steps: Half-Cock → Prime Pan → Charge Barrel → Ram Ball → Full-Cock → Ready to Fire<br>
            Press Reload key to advance through each step. Must be aiming iron sights to fire accurately!
        </p>
        
        <button id="startBtn">BEGIN DUEL</button>
    </div>
    
    <div id="hud1">
        <div class="hud-content">
            <div>PLAYER 1</div>
            <div class="health-bar"><div class="health-fill" id="health1" style="width: 100%"></div></div>
            <div class="reload-indicator">
                State: <span class="state-display" id="state1">UNLOADED</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="hud2">
        <div class="hud-content">
            <div>PLAYER 2</div>
            <div class="health-bar"><div class="health-fill" id="health2" style="width: 100%"></div></div>
            <div class="reload-indicator">
                State: <span class="state-display" id="state2">UNLOADED</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div id="winner">
        <h2 id="winnerText">PLAYER 1 WINS!</h2>
        <button id="restartBtn">DUEL AGAIN</button>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/three.js/r128/three.min.js"></script>
    <script src="controls.js"></script>
    <script src="musket.js"></script>
    <script src="projectile.js"></script>
    <script src="arena.js"></script>
    <script src="player.js"></script>
    <script src="ui.js"></script>
    <script src="game.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
